@page "/help"
@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager

<h1>Help & FAQ</h1>

<div class="help-content">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    
    <h3>1. How do I book an event?</h3>
    <p>To book an event, navigate to the Events page, select the event you're interested in, and click the "Book Now" button. Follow the prompts to complete your booking.</p>

    <h3>2. Can I modify my booking?</h3>
    <p>Yes, you can modify your booking up to 48 hours before the event. Go to "My Events" and select the booking you wish to modify.</p>

    <h3>3. What is the cancellation policy?</h3>
    <p>Cancellations made more than 48 hours before the event are fully refundable. For cancellations within 48 hours, please contact support.</p>

    <h3>4. How do I update my profile information?</h3>
    <p>To update your profile, click on your name in the top right corner and select "Profile" from the dropdown menu. You can edit your information there.</p>

    <h3>5. I'm having trouble logging in. What should I do?</h3>
    <p>If you're having trouble logging in, try resetting your password. If issues persist, please contact our support team at support@kingsinns.com.</p>

    <h2>Need More Help?</h2>
    <p>If you couldn't find the answer to your question, please don't hesitate to contact our support team:</p>
    <p>Email: support@kingsinns.com</p>
    <p>Phone: +353 1 234 5678</p>
    <p>Hours: Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
</div>

